rule.name: Suspicious Microsoft Office Child Process
rule.description: Identifies suspicious child processes of frequently targeted Microsoft Office applications (Word, PowerPoint, Excel). These child processes are often launched during exploitation of Office applications or from documents with malicious macros.

rule.name: Registry Persistence via Microsoft Office Descendant Process
